WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.050 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 3]

02:25.670 --> 02:28.829
These days, I keep telling myself

02:29.710 --> 02:31.510
that after 10 years of marriage,

02:32.070 --> 02:33.240
the bond between us

02:33.240 --> 02:35.190
can't be broken so easily.

02:36.329 --> 02:37.800
This is just a small episode

02:37.800 --> 02:39.079
in our marriage.

02:40.710 --> 02:42.710
Maybe if we had a child,

02:43.840 --> 02:46.079
or if his career was better,

02:47.680 --> 02:51.079
we would be better able to weather
the storms of our marriage.

02:51.360 --> 02:52.560
Life

02:53.310 --> 02:54.590
has to go on.

03:12.320 --> 03:13.000
Hello?

03:16.480 --> 03:17.360
It's today?

03:19.840 --> 03:22.170
Tell Director Wang we'll be there on time.

03:23.680 --> 03:24.430
Gotta go.

03:28.910 --> 03:29.910
Did I wake you up?

03:31.350 --> 03:32.470
I need to go to Ningxin.

03:32.470 --> 03:33.930
I have to leave right away.

03:37.450 --> 03:40.370
Is there any progress
on the project from last time?

03:40.470 --> 03:41.400
I'm not sure yet.

03:41.710 --> 03:43.570
I'll go check it out first and see.

03:43.610 --> 03:45.620
Why don't you eat breakfast
before leaving?

03:45.620 --> 03:46.750
I'll make it for you.

03:50.110 --> 03:52.280
Number 33, Xu Miyu,

03:52.280 --> 03:54.910
Xu Miyu.
Please proceed to Examination Room 4.

03:53.610 --> 03:54.140
[Obstetric First Visit Form]

03:54.140 --> 03:55.460
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Ultrasound Examination Report]

03:56.680 --> 03:58.820
Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
CBC Report

04:02.440 --> 04:03.630
Don't be nervous.

04:05.150 --> 04:05.670
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Ultrasound Examination Report]

04:05.670 --> 04:06.670
[Ultrasound Findings]

04:06.700 --> 04:08.360
[Ultrasound findings: uterine fibroids
and a right adnexal cystic mass.]

04:15.810 --> 04:16.709
It's fine.

04:16.790 --> 04:19.399
Since you get regular checkups,
it should be fine.

04:19.399 --> 04:20.790
This fibroid

04:20.810 --> 04:23.210
is like a pimple on your face.

04:23.340 --> 04:24.690
It won't affect anything.

04:24.690 --> 04:27.320
But I still want to have
a minimally invasive procedure.

04:27.320 --> 04:28.640
That way I will feel more at ease.

04:28.640 --> 04:29.930
Why do you have to make

04:30.080 --> 04:32.500
several cuts in your belly?

04:32.800 --> 04:35.060
I've been trying to get pregnant lately,

04:35.120 --> 04:36.400
but it has not been going well.

04:36.400 --> 04:38.060
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

04:38.060 --> 04:39.350
A lot of women

04:39.409 --> 04:42.120
keep looking for problems in themselves,

04:42.310 --> 04:43.120
and in the end,

04:43.290 --> 04:44.830
there is nothing wrong at all.

04:44.830 --> 04:45.800
Just relax.

04:47.310 --> 04:48.370
Thank you, doctor.

04:51.000 --> 04:51.830
Well...

05:03.680 --> 05:04.360
Miyu,

05:05.010 --> 05:06.740
which one do you like best here?

05:06.750 --> 05:08.010
This one is beautiful.

05:09.020 --> 05:11.400
Actually, I'm not an expert in jewelry,

05:11.470 --> 05:14.450
but if I have to choose,

05:14.630 --> 05:15.810
I would pick this one.

05:15.810 --> 05:16.740
Why?

05:16.920 --> 05:17.750
I value

05:17.750 --> 05:19.630
the reputation of this bracelet's owner.

05:19.630 --> 05:22.240
She should be Ms. Fang Yahui,

05:22.240 --> 05:23.720
a Chinese antique collector.

05:23.720 --> 05:25.950
And although it wasn't made
by a famous master,

05:25.950 --> 05:28.270
I think it's very pure,

05:28.270 --> 05:29.720
the texture is smooth,

05:29.870 --> 05:32.200
and it has the qualities of Zhengkun jade.

05:32.680 --> 05:33.390
How did

05:33.390 --> 05:35.159
that red-glazed vase
Miyu picked for you last time

05:35.159 --> 05:36.070
turn out?

05:36.430 --> 05:37.950
Its market price has doubled.

05:37.950 --> 05:38.720
So?

05:38.840 --> 05:40.440
Miyu knows her stuff, right?

05:40.750 --> 05:43.710
Don't be fooled by her quiet,
domestic side;

05:43.800 --> 05:45.070
she's actually keeping her talents
under wraps.

05:45.070 --> 05:46.200
She's very capable.

05:46.560 --> 05:47.680
That impressive?

05:48.070 --> 05:50.000
It's a real waste of your talents
that you're not

05:50.000 --> 05:51.630
an art appraisal expert.

05:52.800 --> 05:54.430
Are you asking her to do the hard work?

05:54.430 --> 05:56.270
With a husband who dotes on her like that,

05:56.270 --> 05:57.670
it would break his heart.

05:57.770 --> 05:58.190
Yes.

05:58.750 --> 06:00.410
I'll take this jade bracelet.

06:03.980 --> 06:04.820
Yucheng

06:04.890 --> 06:08.350
usually relies on the support
of all of your husbands.

06:08.370 --> 06:11.160
I can't be of much help
with other matters.

06:12.250 --> 06:13.480
If any of you ladies think

06:13.480 --> 06:15.250
I have some talent

06:15.430 --> 06:17.000
in appraising treasures,

06:18.390 --> 06:19.920
feel free to call on me anytime.

06:19.920 --> 06:21.850
I certainly won't hesitate to ask.

06:24.020 --> 06:25.820
I'm going to the restroom first.

06:26.160 --> 06:27.130
I'll go too.

06:27.150 --> 06:28.410
You two keep chatting.

06:32.190 --> 06:33.920
Yucheng was discovered
and promoted

06:33.920 --> 06:35.480
by Mr. Hu, who has a keen eye for talent.

06:35.480 --> 06:37.750
Now that he's at a critical stage
in his career,

06:37.750 --> 06:39.390
he needs Mr. Hu's guidance.

06:42.270 --> 06:43.870
I heard your Nie Yucheng

06:44.310 --> 06:45.750
has a project lately

06:45.770 --> 06:47.430
that's giving him a headache.

06:49.020 --> 06:51.220
I don't ask too much about his work,

06:51.520 --> 06:53.570
But I did hear that

06:53.600 --> 06:55.930
Mr. Hu assigned him a very important task.

06:56.040 --> 06:58.030
We must thank Mr. Hu for his trust.

06:58.240 --> 06:59.550
There's no need for that.
Don't be too formal.

06:59.550 --> 07:01.150
No, we really must thank you.

07:03.610 --> 07:04.200
By the way,

07:04.200 --> 07:05.440
doesn't Mr. Hu like

07:05.460 --> 07:06.790
the braised beef I make?

07:07.050 --> 07:08.530
I'll prepare some more

07:08.560 --> 07:09.830
and bring it over to you.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.070
That's thoughtful of you.

07:11.070 --> 07:13.750
We haven't even finished
what you brought last time.

07:13.750 --> 07:14.750
Nie Yucheng

07:14.840 --> 07:16.400
is so lucky to have a wife

07:16.450 --> 07:18.010
like you.

07:19.680 --> 07:21.000
What are you talking about?

07:21.000 --> 07:22.240
So secretively.

07:22.360 --> 07:23.410
-Exactly.
-What?

07:23.470 --> 07:26.110
Are you afraid
we're gossiping about your Zhang?

07:26.110 --> 07:27.150
Stop it.

07:27.280 --> 07:28.190
Please, keep chatting.

07:28.190 --> 07:29.850
I need to use the restroom too.

07:36.000 --> 07:37.850
You didn't see how she was just now,

07:37.850 --> 07:40.250
acting so submissively for her husband.

07:40.270 --> 07:42.000
I felt sorry just watching her.

07:42.130 --> 07:43.830
Hasn't she found out about Nie Yucheng

07:43.830 --> 07:45.490
and that woman from Yuhua yet?

07:45.500 --> 07:47.430
It's already spread to our circle.

07:47.740 --> 07:49.570
Everyone knows about it.

07:50.120 --> 07:51.600
How could she not know?

07:52.460 --> 07:53.480
Maybe

07:53.480 --> 07:54.810
she's just pretending.

07:55.360 --> 07:57.760
What's so unusual
about this kind of thing?

07:58.060 --> 07:59.800
When a husband has a little affair or two,

07:59.800 --> 08:01.120
you just turn a blind eye

08:01.120 --> 08:02.450
and everything's fine.

08:02.720 --> 08:04.840
Especially in her situation.

08:04.870 --> 08:06.410
She doesn't even have a job.

08:06.800 --> 08:07.720
It's Nie Yucheng

08:07.720 --> 08:09.480
who makes money
to support their whole family.

08:09.480 --> 08:11.190
What could she possibly complain about?

08:11.190 --> 08:12.160
Would she dare

08:12.190 --> 08:14.190
to ask for a divorce?

08:14.190 --> 08:15.190
Exactly.

08:15.680 --> 08:17.510
If a woman who depends on her husband

08:17.510 --> 08:18.750
can't at least be this tolerant,

08:18.750 --> 08:19.610
how will she do?

08:26.720 --> 08:28.750
Mr. Ji, besides the hotels
we just discussed,

08:28.750 --> 08:30.000
Rongshe has also offered

08:30.000 --> 08:31.390
very generous terms.

08:31.390 --> 08:33.520
They're willing to give you 5% equity.

08:33.840 --> 08:34.600
Then...

08:35.320 --> 08:36.840
what about the Purong Hotel?

08:36.840 --> 08:39.299
Purong Hotel may be an old hotel
in Shanghai,

08:39.900 --> 08:42.360
but ever since Mr. Wei retired 6 years ago

08:42.640 --> 08:45.080
and his nephew Wei Siyuan
took over as general manager,

08:45.080 --> 08:47.470
it has been going downhill
year after year.

08:47.470 --> 08:48.620
Not only have there been
constant negative stories

08:48.620 --> 08:51.040
about financial scandals
and external crises,

08:51.040 --> 08:53.570
they also have not achieved
any real results.

08:54.120 --> 08:54.750
I don't think

08:54.750 --> 08:56.960
it's the best choice for you.

08:56.960 --> 08:58.630
Although their offer is generous

08:58.630 --> 09:00.710
and they promise you the position
of general manager,

09:00.710 --> 09:02.510
the conditions are quite harsh.

09:03.160 --> 09:04.240
What are these?

09:05.150 --> 09:06.390
The hotel has already sent
the relevant information

09:06.390 --> 09:07.630
to your email.

09:07.630 --> 09:09.510
You can take some time to review it.

09:09.510 --> 09:11.790
They're giving you one year
as general manager.

09:11.790 --> 09:12.960
Only if the hotel

09:12.960 --> 09:14.960
achieves over 30% profit growth
during that year

09:13.660 --> 09:14.560
[Inbox]

09:14.740 --> 09:16.390
[Mr. Ji Feng, we sincerely invite you to
serve as General Manager of Purong Hotel.]

09:15.270 --> 09:17.240
will the previously mentioned terms
take effect.

09:17.240 --> 09:18.240
And if it doesn't?

09:18.250 --> 09:21.290
[Sales Report of Purong Hotel]

09:18.870 --> 09:19.960
Then you leave.

09:20.600 --> 09:23.270
If you're considering
taking on such a difficult role,

09:23.270 --> 09:25.480
do you have any other conditions?

09:25.750 --> 09:26.390
After one year,

09:26.390 --> 09:28.840
I want 10% of Purong Hotel's shares.

09:30.750 --> 09:32.910
[Ningxin]

09:33.910 --> 09:34.770
Director Wang.

09:35.240 --> 09:36.100
Director Wang.

09:36.200 --> 09:37.000
Nie.

09:37.630 --> 09:38.440
Thank you so much

09:38.440 --> 09:41.480
for giving us the opportunity
with the Yufeng Jiangnan project.

09:41.480 --> 09:42.840
You don't need to thank me.

09:42.840 --> 09:44.440
I was just pressured

09:44.510 --> 09:46.110
by Zhen until I had no choice.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.270
If you want to thank someone,

09:47.270 --> 09:48.330
thank her instead.

09:48.570 --> 09:50.620
Zhen? You mean Lu Zhenzhen?

09:51.120 --> 09:52.830
Yes, she's my goddaughter.

09:54.910 --> 09:55.960
She never told you?

09:55.960 --> 09:56.770
No, she didn't.

09:56.770 --> 09:58.820
Her father and I are old classmates.

09:59.240 --> 10:01.060
This time, for your matter,

10:01.080 --> 10:03.170
goodness, she called me every day.

10:03.600 --> 10:05.200
I've never heard her

10:05.440 --> 10:07.640
speak to me in such a sweet voice before.

10:13.270 --> 10:13.840
Mr. Yang.

10:15.240 --> 10:15.840
Feng.

10:17.630 --> 10:18.480
Feng.

10:19.360 --> 10:20.320
Our Yuhua

10:20.320 --> 10:22.270
will need your and Mr. Nie's support
in the future.

10:22.270 --> 10:24.240
Please include us in any future projects.

10:24.240 --> 10:25.250
Don't mention it.

10:25.510 --> 10:26.480
We're old friends.

10:26.480 --> 10:27.080
Come on, bottoms up!

10:27.080 --> 10:27.540
Cheers.

10:27.720 --> 10:27.910
Here.

10:27.910 --> 10:28.240
Okay.

10:32.640 --> 10:33.310
Zhen.

10:33.790 --> 10:35.190
Why aren't you drinking?

10:35.290 --> 10:36.210
Yes, Zhen.

10:36.720 --> 10:38.290
You should toast to Feng too.

10:38.290 --> 10:39.740
Feng, my alcohol tolerance

10:39.740 --> 10:41.340
isn't very good, I'm afraid.

10:42.510 --> 10:43.570
Just have a little.

10:43.840 --> 10:44.840
Just as a gesture.

10:46.510 --> 10:47.040
Alright.

10:50.270 --> 10:50.730
Come on.

10:53.270 --> 10:55.200
Don't drink if you can't handle it.

10:56.240 --> 10:56.790
How about this?

10:56.790 --> 10:58.270
Mr. Feng, let me toast you.

10:58.270 --> 10:59.440
No, please don't.

10:59.440 --> 11:01.030
-Boss, we won't let her drink anymore.
-Mr. Nie.

11:01.030 --> 11:01.670
Come on.

11:01.750 --> 11:02.480
Have a seat.

11:04.700 --> 11:05.410
Sit.

11:06.360 --> 11:06.910
Sit.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.800
Waiter, bring another chair.

11:09.800 --> 11:11.130
And a few more drinks.

11:12.870 --> 11:13.790
Thank you for helping me.

11:13.790 --> 11:14.910
Let's drink.

11:14.910 --> 11:15.720
Let's drink.

11:34.950 --> 11:36.980
[Zhenhai District] [Hongkou District]

11:44.730 --> 11:45.930
Men change their hearts

11:45.930 --> 11:47.960
just like phone upgrades.

11:48.150 --> 11:49.720
It's perfectly normal.

11:50.120 --> 11:52.250
Especially in her situation.

11:52.330 --> 11:53.550
She doesn't even have a job.

11:53.550 --> 11:54.510
It's Nie Yucheng

11:54.510 --> 11:56.320
who makes money
to support their whole family.

11:56.320 --> 11:57.670
What could she possibly complain about?

11:57.670 --> 11:59.790
Would she dare to ask for a divorce?

11:59.810 --> 12:00.910
I, Nie Yucheng,

12:01.360 --> 12:02.920
have been working hard all this time

12:02.920 --> 12:04.050
for only one reason—

12:04.260 --> 12:05.070
you.

12:13.630 --> 12:13.980
[Minfu Bank]

12:14.000 --> 12:14.670
[Minfu Bank Expenditure]

12:14.690 --> 12:15.740
[Transfer via online banking: 150,000 RMB]

12:32.110 --> 12:34.080
Welcome home.

12:41.570 --> 12:43.640
I'm finally home.

12:44.350 --> 12:46.210
Nothing like the comfort of home.

12:53.780 --> 12:54.580
What's wrong?

12:55.000 --> 12:56.040
Have you been drinking?

12:56.040 --> 12:56.840
No, I haven't.

12:58.080 --> 12:59.440
I drove all the way back.

12:59.440 --> 13:00.600
How could I drink?

13:01.390 --> 13:03.200
Aren't you being a bit paranoid?

13:05.370 --> 13:06.240
Did Minghui...

13:07.080 --> 13:08.680
borrow money from you again?

13:10.020 --> 13:11.280
You mean that 150,000?

13:11.910 --> 13:12.480
Yes.

13:13.360 --> 13:15.240
He said his family urgently needs money

13:15.240 --> 13:16.730
and asked me for a temporary loan.

13:16.730 --> 13:17.490
I'm sorry.

13:18.270 --> 13:20.530
I lent it to him without asking you first.

13:21.120 --> 13:22.670
What happened with his family?

13:22.670 --> 13:23.660
Their family...

13:23.790 --> 13:25.840
Either his wife Ting has issues today

13:25.840 --> 13:27.900
or he himself has problems tomorrow.

13:28.080 --> 13:30.140
They're basically drowning in debt.

13:35.030 --> 13:35.890
How about this?

13:37.080 --> 13:38.120
I'll ask him

13:38.270 --> 13:39.510
exactly why he needed to borrow money.

13:39.510 --> 13:40.340
Forget it.

13:40.630 --> 13:43.350
If you call him, he'll think
you don't want to lend him the money.

13:43.350 --> 13:44.080
That's true.

13:44.550 --> 13:45.680
With lending money,

13:45.750 --> 13:47.210
either you do it directly,

13:47.240 --> 13:48.390
or don't do it at all.

13:49.030 --> 13:49.840
How about this?

13:49.840 --> 13:51.080
When he pays it back,

13:51.270 --> 13:53.270
I'll ask about the whole situation.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.740
I'm going to take a shower now.

14:27.480 --> 14:28.200
Yucheng.

14:29.320 --> 14:30.080
Yucheng.

14:31.150 --> 14:33.210
Yucheng, time to take your medicine.

14:37.250 --> 14:38.620
[Jane]

14:41.280 --> 14:44.470
Can't sleep. I miss your scent.

14:41.360 --> 14:44.230
[Jane]

14:47.440 --> 14:48.370
Hello, Mr. Yang.

14:48.840 --> 14:49.570
This is Zhen.

15:36.570 --> 15:37.690
Ting,

15:37.750 --> 15:40.550
has Minghui been going through
something lately?

15:40.630 --> 15:42.200
Does he urgently need money?

15:42.200 --> 15:43.510
What money, Miyu?

15:42.790 --> 15:46.220
[Upgrade to Premium Membership
to enjoy eore benefits]

15:43.720 --> 15:45.980
Did Minghui ask to borrow money from you?

15:46.260 --> 15:47.550
[Inbox
[Liu Minghui]

15:47.570 --> 15:49.090
[Liu Minghui's Medical Expenses]

15:49.120 --> 15:51.150
[Sales Department Report Records]

15:51.150 --> 15:51.860
[Medical Expenses]

15:53.100 --> 15:54.040
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Billing Statement]

15:55.280 --> 15:56.160
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Billing Statement]

15:59.770 --> 16:01.650
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Billing Statement]

16:09.540 --> 16:12.430
[Total: 150,000 yuan]

16:48.790 --> 16:49.240
Miss!

16:49.630 --> 16:50.890
Are you alright, miss?

16:53.440 --> 16:54.500
Are you okay, miss?

16:57.490 --> 16:58.080
Miss!

17:09.030 --> 17:10.030
How is the baby?

17:10.510 --> 17:11.910
The baby is very healthy.

17:12.109 --> 17:13.420
And quite active too.

17:15.810 --> 17:16.550
Let me.

17:22.760 --> 17:23.200
Okay.

17:23.250 --> 17:24.310
Thank you, doctor.

17:24.400 --> 17:24.750
Okay.

17:24.750 --> 17:25.810
We're leaving now.

17:26.000 --> 17:26.530
Goodbye.

17:26.560 --> 17:27.119
Bye.

17:28.680 --> 17:31.100
Not in a hurry
to distance yourself from me now?

17:31.100 --> 17:33.500
Not afraid I'll be a bad influence
anymore?

17:34.280 --> 17:37.610
[Reception]

17:34.860 --> 17:36.990
I was just talking out of anger before.

17:37.350 --> 17:38.480
Let me take you home.

17:38.510 --> 17:39.160
No.

17:39.160 --> 17:40.550
I've arranged a city walk with a client

17:40.550 --> 17:41.640
on Shaanxi South Road.

17:41.640 --> 17:42.640
Then don't drink.

17:43.110 --> 17:45.510
If I don't drink,
who's going to support me?

17:45.720 --> 17:47.020
I will.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.020
Don't be silly.

17:48.200 --> 17:49.310
I will.

17:49.310 --> 17:50.480
Stop it.

17:50.480 --> 17:51.750
Will you let me or not?

17:52.260 --> 17:53.440
You're so annoying.

18:03.530 --> 18:04.730
Why do you have to make

18:04.920 --> 18:07.540
several cuts in your belly?

18:08.920 --> 18:11.190
I've been trying to get pregnant lately,

18:11.310 --> 18:12.970
but it has not been going well.

18:13.110 --> 18:15.040
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

18:15.040 --> 18:16.070
Just relax.

18:41.590 --> 18:42.720
I also used to dream

18:43.110 --> 18:45.110
that my life

18:45.110 --> 18:47.240
could have limitless possibilities.

18:47.680 --> 18:50.400
I wanted a happy, carefree life

18:51.200 --> 18:53.310
and to be a person of value.

18:54.280 --> 18:56.030
I thought that as long as I

18:56.030 --> 18:57.560
managed our marriage well,

18:58.480 --> 19:00.310
I could achieve all of that.

19:01.330 --> 19:03.200
But now I finally see

19:04.960 --> 19:06.200
how unrealistic

19:06.200 --> 19:08.070
my pursuit was.

19:10.840 --> 19:14.230
From the day I gave up myself for you,

19:15.670 --> 19:18.800
there was no such thing
as a perfect marriage anymore.

19:20.480 --> 19:22.240
Between two people who no longer

19:22.240 --> 19:23.640
share the same rhythm,

19:24.510 --> 19:26.940
even if Lu Zhenzhen isn't around today,

19:27.310 --> 19:29.240
there will be Wang Zhenzhen,

19:29.240 --> 19:30.500
Li Zhenzhen tomorrow.

19:31.070 --> 19:33.600
What's scary isn't that
I chose the wrong man,

19:34.350 --> 19:36.210
but that from the very beginning,

19:37.000 --> 19:39.070
I bet on the wrong life.

19:47.510 --> 19:48.750
Hello, is this Mr. Su?

19:51.200 --> 19:52.720
I'm coming to see you now.

19:53.140 --> 19:54.630
[Attorney: Su Xiaoning]

19:54.710 --> 19:56.080
[Divorce Agreement]

19:56.110 --> 19:56.580
[Hengzheng Law Firm]

19:56.580 --> 19:57.530
[Attorney: Su Xiaoning]

20:00.510 --> 20:01.640
Based on the information

20:01.640 --> 20:03.520
about your husband's financial situation,

20:03.060 --> 20:03.780
[Vehicles] [Other Assets]

20:03.780 --> 20:08.320
[Financial Support and Compensation for Emotional Distress]
[Application for Divorce Certificate]

20:03.960 --> 20:05.400
I've drafted an agreement.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.270
Take a look.

20:07.110 --> 20:09.910
Aside from the joint assets
we already know about,

20:10.050 --> 20:12.840
the savings and investments
he hid from me—

20:13.140 --> 20:14.210
legally,

20:14.240 --> 20:15.400
they should also count

20:15.400 --> 20:16.880
as our marital property, right?

20:16.880 --> 20:17.550
Of course.

20:18.420 --> 20:19.110
Any income

20:19.110 --> 20:21.030
earned during your marriage

20:21.170 --> 20:22.550
would be divided equally

20:22.550 --> 20:24.550
if you divorce.

20:25.110 --> 20:26.310
And morally,

20:26.830 --> 20:29.030
it's not too much to ask for this, right?

20:30.560 --> 20:31.240
I deal with

20:31.240 --> 20:33.020
all kinds of couples every day.

20:33.790 --> 20:35.650
No matter how good they were once,

20:35.960 --> 20:37.890
once they decide to take this step,

20:38.750 --> 20:39.680
it's war.

20:44.450 --> 20:48.290
[Husband's Fingerprint]
[Wife's Fingerprint]

20:45.160 --> 20:46.070
Ms. Xu,

20:46.720 --> 20:48.590
are you sure about this decision?

20:57.080 --> 20:58.670
[Purong Hotel]

21:01.900 --> 21:03.410
[Purong Hotel]

21:04.050 --> 21:05.540
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

21:12.790 --> 21:13.750
I see you've

21:13.750 --> 21:15.680
booked a luxury king room.

21:15.680 --> 21:17.750
-I will...
-Give me room 1819.

21:21.400 --> 21:22.540
I'm sorry, ma'am.

21:22.670 --> 21:24.750
The guest in room 1819 just checked out.

21:24.750 --> 21:26.880
-It's still being cleaned.
-Room key.

21:27.110 --> 21:27.680
Alright.

21:30.140 --> 21:32.450
You can wait at the coffee bar...

21:33.590 --> 21:34.280
nearby.

21:36.070 --> 21:38.160
Why does this guest look so distressed?

21:38.160 --> 21:40.560
Have the HSKP Department
keep an eye on her.

21:42.360 --> 21:45.400
Why do I feel like
I've seen her somewhere before?

22:55.510 --> 22:57.140
Hello, how may I help you?

22:58.880 --> 22:59.590
Welcome.

22:59.590 --> 23:01.120
Make sure you get some rest.

23:29.060 --> 23:34.350
[Honey]

23:32.600 --> 23:33.350
Honey,

23:33.590 --> 23:34.520
you're not home?

23:36.440 --> 23:37.790
There's a project celebration banquet
tonight.

23:37.790 --> 23:38.590
You must come.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.680
All our partners will be there,

23:41.680 --> 23:44.210
and everyone says
they really want to see you.

23:44.750 --> 23:45.880
I've sent you the location.

23:45.880 --> 23:47.210
Take your time. No rush.

23:47.550 --> 23:49.460
[Honey]

23:48.360 --> 23:49.390
Love you, see.

23:51.130 --> 23:52.980
[Honey]

23:51.880 --> 23:52.810
Love you, Honey.

24:07.640 --> 24:09.630
Break up. One phrase. Two words.

24:10.630 --> 24:12.980
It only takes a second to say.

24:13.340 --> 24:14.740
But you didn't.

24:15.830 --> 24:17.310
The thought of you and Lu Zhenzhen

24:17.310 --> 24:19.680
touching, kissing,

24:19.700 --> 24:21.700
and writhing together like animals

24:22.160 --> 24:24.200
right here on this bed

24:25.830 --> 24:27.340
makes me resolute.

25:06.090 --> 25:08.340
[Mingmei Obstetrics and Gynecology Hospital
Billing Statement]

25:20.050 --> 25:20.460
[Hello, Ms. Lu Zhenzhen.]

25:20.490 --> 25:21.310
[We sincerely invite you to attend]

25:21.330 --> 25:22.130
[the celebration banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan project.]

25:30.260 --> 25:31.610
[Theme: Invitation to the Yufeng Jiangnan Project
Celebration Banquet]

25:31.870 --> 25:32.860
[Sending]

25:39.310 --> 25:40.680
The Yufeng Jiangnan project,

25:40.680 --> 25:42.030
whether for Changyang

25:42.030 --> 25:43.310
or for me personally,

25:43.310 --> 25:45.030
is the top priority this year.

25:45.030 --> 25:46.200
This is a key project.

25:46.200 --> 25:48.550
The fact that
it has progressed smoothly to this point

25:48.550 --> 25:50.680
is thanks most of all to everyone here.

25:50.680 --> 25:51.510
Thank you all

25:51.830 --> 25:52.680
for your support,

25:52.680 --> 25:53.720
encouragement, and cooperation.

25:53.720 --> 25:54.510
To our cooperation.

25:54.510 --> 25:55.270
Come on.

25:55.300 --> 25:56.440
-To our cooperation.
-To our cooperation.

25:56.440 --> 25:57.680
Thank you, everyone.

25:57.680 --> 25:58.310
Thank you.

25:58.310 --> 25:59.000
Thank you, Mr. Li.

25:59.000 --> 25:59.510
Here's to our cooperation.

25:59.510 --> 26:01.910
-To our cooperation.
-To our cooperation.

26:04.030 --> 26:04.830
Thank you.

26:04.850 --> 26:05.860
Please, have a seat.

26:05.860 --> 26:06.420
Mr. Nie.

26:06.810 --> 26:08.030
Will Mrs. Nie be joining us today?

26:08.030 --> 26:09.090
Yes, she's coming.

26:09.310 --> 26:10.240
She should be here soon.

26:10.240 --> 26:10.870
Let me ask her.

26:10.460 --> 26:12.220
[Honey]

26:11.720 --> 26:12.520
Let me tell you.

26:12.260 --> 26:15.430
[Where are you?]

26:12.830 --> 26:14.330
I heard a long time ago
that Mr. Nie's wife

26:14.330 --> 26:16.810
-Where are you?
-is said to bring him good fortune.

26:16.810 --> 26:19.170
If we can see Mrs. Nie here today,

26:19.310 --> 26:20.720
it will be our honor.

26:20.720 --> 26:21.440
Indeed.

26:21.480 --> 26:22.510
You're too kind.

26:22.510 --> 26:23.310
I've never seen her before.

26:23.310 --> 26:24.000
Wonderful.

26:26.640 --> 26:27.280
Mrs. Nie.

26:28.340 --> 26:29.720
She's so elegant.

26:30.050 --> 26:31.180
She's so beautiful.

26:31.800 --> 26:32.490
Honey.

26:33.500 --> 26:35.030
Let me introduce everyone.

26:35.110 --> 26:36.680
This is my wife, Xu Miyu.

26:37.030 --> 26:37.920
I'm sorry

26:37.920 --> 26:38.800
for being late.

26:39.350 --> 26:40.880
Mr. Nie is truly a lucky man.

26:40.890 --> 26:41.920
-Thank you. Thank you.
-Yes. Yes.

26:41.920 --> 26:42.740
You're a lucky man, Mr. Nie.

26:42.740 --> 26:44.690
Let's propose a toast as a couple.

26:44.960 --> 26:45.550
Okay.

26:45.550 --> 26:46.050
Here.

26:46.480 --> 26:47.550
To our cooperation, everyone.

26:47.550 --> 26:48.590
-To our cooperation.
-To our cooperation.

26:48.590 --> 26:49.270
Cheers.

26:49.290 --> 26:50.070
To our cooperation.

26:50.070 --> 26:51.670
You're such a perfect match.

26:55.850 --> 26:56.710
Come, sit down.

26:58.710 --> 26:59.360
Here.

27:02.310 --> 27:04.110
You usually don't eat crab

27:04.110 --> 27:05.300
because of me.

27:05.830 --> 27:08.130
Try the crab here and see how it tastes.

27:11.110 --> 27:12.370
Who ordered this crab?

27:13.550 --> 27:15.410
This is considered a "cold" food.

27:15.920 --> 27:18.250
Aren't you worried about harming the baby?

27:18.250 --> 27:19.070
Mr. Nie!

27:19.240 --> 27:20.880
You've got double happiness!

27:20.880 --> 27:21.880
Congratulations, Boss.

27:21.880 --> 27:23.110
When did this happen, Boss?

27:23.110 --> 27:24.540
Why didn't you tell us?

27:24.600 --> 27:25.260
Mrs. Nie...

27:25.680 --> 27:27.050
Don't make such a fuss.

27:27.110 --> 27:27.600
Eat up.

27:27.620 --> 27:29.020
-Eat up.
-It's good news.

27:29.120 --> 27:30.230
Let's eat.

27:30.770 --> 27:33.310
Minghui, how are things with your family?

27:33.360 --> 27:34.760
Is 150,000 enough?

27:35.770 --> 27:36.330
Yes.

27:36.760 --> 27:37.620
It's enough.

27:37.980 --> 27:39.260
Let me know if it's not enough.

27:39.260 --> 27:41.060
I've checked Mingmei's prices.

27:41.150 --> 27:43.000
If it's natural birth
plus postpartum care center,

27:43.000 --> 27:44.110
150,000 is enough.

27:44.550 --> 27:46.110
But if it's a C-section,

27:46.110 --> 27:47.170
it might cost more.

27:51.130 --> 27:52.990
Let's not discuss this in public.

27:55.240 --> 27:56.590
Does everyone really not know?

27:56.590 --> 27:57.680
Today is Mr. Nie's

27:57.680 --> 27:59.310
day of double happiness.

28:00.350 --> 28:01.350
He'll be a father.

28:02.790 --> 28:03.640
Hello, everyone.

28:03.640 --> 28:05.040
I'm sorry for being late.

28:17.230 --> 28:18.790
Sorry, I came to the wrong room.

28:18.790 --> 28:20.920
Lu Zhenzhen, why are you running away?

28:22.560 --> 28:23.450
I'm not.

28:25.230 --> 28:25.990
Mrs. Nie,

28:26.440 --> 28:28.370
I'm leaving out of respect for you.

28:30.590 --> 28:31.790
Out of respect for me?

28:33.050 --> 28:34.450
That sounds ridiculous.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.440
As if I'm the mistress.

28:36.780 --> 28:37.860
The mistress?

28:41.380 --> 28:43.840
Mr. Yang, she's from Yuhua, right?

28:44.050 --> 28:45.180
Sorry, everyone.

28:45.210 --> 28:46.240
My wife is drunk.

28:46.260 --> 28:46.880
I'll take her home.

28:46.880 --> 28:47.680
-I haven't drunk it.
-Let's go.

28:47.680 --> 28:49.680
-How can I be drunk?
-You're drunk. Let's go home, alright?

28:49.680 --> 28:50.480
Let go of me!

28:50.480 --> 28:51.520
Let go of me!

28:51.600 --> 28:52.410
Let go!

28:54.750 --> 28:55.920
What's wrong with you?

28:55.920 --> 28:58.180
You're scared, aren't you, Nie Yucheng?

28:58.310 --> 28:59.270
You've gotten used to

28:59.270 --> 29:01.800
the Xu Miyu who always reads your mood
and acts accordingly,

29:01.800 --> 29:03.720
who acts in front of your bosses
and colleagues

29:03.720 --> 29:05.550
as the perfect,

29:05.550 --> 29:06.750
understanding wife.

29:07.960 --> 29:09.310
But this Xu Miyu in front of you

29:09.310 --> 29:12.040
makes you feel like
you can't control her, right?

29:14.570 --> 29:15.470
Let me tell you.

29:16.110 --> 29:17.410
From today on,

29:17.850 --> 29:19.000
everything I do,

29:19.000 --> 29:20.160
every word I say,

29:20.160 --> 29:21.400
I won't be trying to please you anymore.

29:21.400 --> 29:23.440
I won't care if you're happy or not.

29:24.730 --> 29:25.810
I'll only care

29:26.400 --> 29:27.310
if I'm happy.

29:34.250 --> 29:35.290
Miss Lu.

29:36.040 --> 29:37.000
How's the baby?

29:38.800 --> 29:40.730
Did the prenatal check-up go well?

29:48.430 --> 29:49.360
Don't be afraid.

29:49.460 --> 29:51.460
I just want to take a good look at you.

29:54.240 --> 29:55.090
Indeed.

29:56.900 --> 29:57.900
Young,

29:58.670 --> 29:59.510
beautiful,

30:00.710 --> 30:01.790
cunning,

30:03.000 --> 30:04.400
and without principles.

30:05.420 --> 30:07.090
What's that saying again?

30:05.460 --> 30:06.570
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

30:08.360 --> 30:11.620
The lower someone goes,
the more unstoppable they become.

30:12.160 --> 30:12.990
That's right.

30:14.070 --> 30:16.200
But your taste isn't very good.

30:17.190 --> 30:18.350
The person you've fallen for

30:18.350 --> 30:20.610
is a highly polished, self-serving man.

30:21.350 --> 30:24.660
If you're not even more calculating
than he is,

30:24.780 --> 30:25.680
I'm afraid

30:25.700 --> 30:26.880
it won't end well

30:28.070 --> 30:29.980
if you stay with him.

30:34.040 --> 30:35.430
Nie Yucheng, am I right?

30:35.580 --> 30:39.950
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

30:36.480 --> 30:38.480
How many years have we been married?

30:39.120 --> 30:40.400
Ten years, right?

30:41.730 --> 30:43.210
Time flies.

30:44.450 --> 30:46.850
In the blink of an eye,
10 years have passed.

30:47.360 --> 30:48.570
Actually, I've always known

30:48.570 --> 30:50.460
that you're a selfish person.

30:50.720 --> 30:52.230
You said you had stomach problems,

30:52.230 --> 30:53.480
so I willingly

30:53.510 --> 30:55.640
became a housewife for 10 years,

30:55.880 --> 30:57.880
preparing meals for you,

30:57.900 --> 31:00.370
and supporting you every step of the way
as your career advanced.

31:00.370 --> 31:01.810
Do you know why?

31:03.970 --> 31:05.030
Because I love you.

31:05.140 --> 31:06.820
I love our family.

31:07.010 --> 31:09.000
Miyu, can we not do this he—

31:09.320 --> 31:11.740
Until I saw with my own eyes
how you trampled on my dignity

31:11.740 --> 31:13.530
with another woman.

31:16.630 --> 31:17.770
I came here today

31:19.110 --> 31:20.890
to reclaim

31:21.320 --> 31:22.820
the dignity I've lost,

31:25.850 --> 31:27.020
to reclaim the self

31:27.300 --> 31:29.780
that doesn't even exist in your eyes.

31:32.490 --> 31:33.540
Nie Yucheng,

31:34.810 --> 31:36.000
let's get divorced.

31:41.340 --> 31:43.770
[Celebration Banquet
for the Yufeng Jiangnan Project]

31:57.070 --> 31:57.840
Xu Miyu.

32:00.080 --> 32:00.990
Xu Miyu!

32:01.990 --> 32:03.500
What exactly are you trying to do?

32:03.500 --> 32:05.160
The room was full of my business partners.

32:05.160 --> 32:07.310
Why did you say those things
in front of them?

32:07.310 --> 32:07.980
Why?

32:08.120 --> 32:08.750
You have no shame,

32:08.750 --> 32:09.660
but I do!

32:09.810 --> 32:11.210
Don't you want a divorce?

32:11.370 --> 32:12.890
What gives you the right to divorce me?

32:12.890 --> 32:14.660
What makes you think you can divorce me?

32:14.660 --> 32:16.490
Do you think you'll have a good life
after divorcing me?

32:16.490 --> 32:17.410
You won't!

32:17.550 --> 32:18.890
You're nothing but a parasite!

32:18.890 --> 32:20.550
Your whole family is the same!

32:27.960 --> 32:28.720
Xu Miyu!

32:30.700 --> 32:32.230
Let's see how far you can go!

32:33.140 --> 32:35.870
If you're so capable,
don't come back begging me!

32:49.360 --> 32:51.470
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

32:52.430 --> 32:54.450
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

32:56.320 --> 32:58.590
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

32:59.640 --> 33:01.550
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

33:03.370 --> 33:05.690
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

33:06.220 --> 33:08.360
♪ In the virtual world ♪

33:09.710 --> 33:15.230
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

33:16.650 --> 33:18.470
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

33:19.050 --> 33:22.280
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

33:22.160 --> 33:23.940
What makes you think you can divorce me?

33:23.940 --> 33:25.530
♪ Until I met you ♪

33:24.210 --> 33:26.070
Do you think you'll have a good life
after divorcing me?

33:26.070 --> 33:26.960
You won't!

33:26.330 --> 33:29.430
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

33:30.010 --> 33:31.800
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

33:32.430 --> 33:34.090
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

33:33.880 --> 33:35.160
You're nothing but a parasite!

33:34.530 --> 33:35.760
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

33:35.180 --> 33:36.530
Your whole family is the same!

33:36.250 --> 33:37.950
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

33:38.280 --> 33:41.330
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

33:41.410 --> 33:45.190
[For dramatic effect only. Do not imitate]

33:41.720 --> 33:43.190
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

33:44.280 --> 33:45.970
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

33:46.270 --> 33:47.660
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

33:48.740 --> 33:50.780
♪ Love really hurts ♪

33:52.170 --> 33:56.520
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

34:09.469 --> 34:11.320
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

34:11.770 --> 34:15.130
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

34:16.760 --> 34:18.380
♪ Until I met you ♪

34:19.150 --> 34:22.210
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

34:22.980 --> 34:24.850
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

34:25.290 --> 34:27.020
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

34:27.460 --> 34:28.719
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

34:29.070 --> 34:30.840
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

34:30.840 --> 34:31.800
Xu Miyu?

34:31.250 --> 34:34.270
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

34:34.600 --> 34:36.070
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

34:36.880 --> 34:37.889
Li Qiaoqi?

34:37.219 --> 34:38.730
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

34:39.080 --> 34:40.730
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

34:39.110 --> 34:39.920
Hop on.

34:41.670 --> 34:43.719
♪ Love really hurts ♪

34:44.830 --> 34:49.500
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

34:52.989 --> 34:55.710
♪ Only when you've been hurt by love
do you realize how crazy you once were ♪

34:56.210 --> 34:59.130
♪ A beautiful dream
turns into a nightmare in an instant ♪

34:56.739 --> 34:57.660
Qiaoqi,

34:57.880 --> 34:59.620
the road is wet and slippery. Ride slowly.

34:59.620 --> 35:01.370
It's okay. Hold on tight!

35:00.380 --> 35:05.270
♪ You are a neon light
I could never catch ♪

35:04.190 --> 35:06.150
We're taking off!

35:06.180 --> 35:08.400
Li Qiaoqi, slow down!

35:06.240 --> 35:08.160
♪ I loved you recklessly ♪

35:08.430 --> 35:09.320
I'm scared!

35:09.320 --> 35:12.710
Li Qiaoqi is taking off with Xu Miyu!

35:09.540 --> 35:11.910
♪ And ended up covered in wounds ♪

35:13.040 --> 35:14.270
♪ Yet I still believe in ♪

35:15.280 --> 35:17.590
♪ The sky after the rain ♪

35:19.430 --> 35:21.430
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

35:21.800 --> 35:23.430
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

35:23.970 --> 35:25.230
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

35:25.580 --> 35:27.340
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

35:27.750 --> 35:30.780
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

35:31.110 --> 35:32.580
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

35:33.720 --> 35:35.230
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

35:35.590 --> 35:37.230
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

35:38.180 --> 35:40.230
♪ Love really hurts ♪

35:41.340 --> 35:46.010
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

35:49.160 --> 35:54.390
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

35:50.600 --> 35:54.330
[Breakfast Service: 06:30]

35:53.790 --> 35:55.390
What's wrong? Feeling down?

36:00.780 --> 36:02.510
When did you come back to China?

36:02.910 --> 36:04.310
I've been back for a year.

36:04.400 --> 36:06.800
I've been working as a chef
at Purong Hotel.

36:09.340 --> 36:11.070
So your dream really came true?

36:11.510 --> 36:13.640
Working as a chef at a five-star hotel?

36:13.850 --> 36:14.550
That's wonderful.

36:14.550 --> 36:15.880
I'm just the sous-chef.

36:17.190 --> 36:19.670
But if you stayed at our hotel this year,

36:19.690 --> 36:22.090
you might have actually tasted my cooking.

36:25.630 --> 36:26.940
Listen to me rambling.

36:27.360 --> 36:28.760
You have your own house here.

36:28.760 --> 36:30.490
Why would you stay at our hotel?

36:35.760 --> 36:36.760
Where do you live?

36:36.810 --> 36:38.070
I rented an apartment.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.470
It's not far from Purong.

36:41.260 --> 36:43.120
The rent must be expensive there.

36:43.360 --> 36:45.230
Not really. I live alone,

36:45.260 --> 36:46.730
spending my own money as I please.

36:46.730 --> 36:47.930
You're still single?

36:48.630 --> 36:49.890
I prefer being single.

36:50.070 --> 36:52.400
Another person just complicates things.

36:54.630 --> 36:55.510
I shouldn't be

36:55.510 --> 36:56.960
putting these toxic ideas in your head.

36:56.960 --> 36:58.500
You're so family-oriented.

36:58.500 --> 37:01.160
You should go home
and take care of your husband.

37:11.190 --> 37:11.920
Qiaoqi.

37:12.960 --> 37:14.150
Thank you for today.

37:14.560 --> 37:17.150
It's so wonderful to see you again.

37:17.340 --> 37:19.080
Why are you being so formal today?

37:19.080 --> 37:20.860
You were never this reserved before.

37:20.860 --> 37:23.260
Marriage didn't mess up your brain,
did it?

37:24.850 --> 37:25.690
Maybe.

37:27.220 --> 37:28.670
Then you've met the right person.

37:28.670 --> 37:30.650
I'll take you out more when I have time,

37:30.650 --> 37:31.890
just like when we were kids.

37:31.890 --> 37:32.740
It's a deal then.

37:32.740 --> 37:34.450
I'll be waiting for your invitation.

37:34.450 --> 37:36.110
Let's go. I'll give you a ride.

38:00.770 --> 38:05.610
[Divorce Agreement]

38:06.860 --> 38:09.150
[Husband's Fingerprint]
[Wife's Fingerprint]

38:14.850 --> 38:15.600
Stop.

38:28.630 --> 38:29.740
Sign this before you leave.

38:29.740 --> 38:30.600
You're really going to do this?

38:30.600 --> 38:31.730
I've already signed it.

38:31.730 --> 38:32.560
All that's left is your signature.
